description:
&lt;p&gt;We are offering a fantastic opportunity to be part of the patient feedback team within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for individuals with outstanding communication abilities, a range of computer skills and who are experienced in providing customer care. Excellent interpersonal skills, a friendly approach, enthusiasm and motivation are all required for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience of working with an emphasis on customer service would be desirable, as this post entails handling patient feedback . We require the candidates to be able to manage their own timescales and deadlines effectively and therefore will need to evidence good organisation skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not reapply. This post will close once sufficient applications are received.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jo Loughborough, Lead Nurse Patient Experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address joanna.loughborough@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number030333030091&lt;/p&gt;
